high_descs: Grab the watch out of the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Grab a watch and turn a lamp on.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white dresser in the corner.
Take a watch from the bottom left dresser drawer.
Look up at the lamp on the corner of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Look at a watch under the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Walk around the corner of the bed to the white dresser.
Take the watch out of the lower left drawer of the dresser.
Turn upwards to face the lamp on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Look at a watch by the light of a lit lamp.
